{"tid":979144,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[沙盒RPG]Hytale集中討論(1) Minecraft+Subnautica+Cubeworld進化版","createTime":"2019-01-12T13:18:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-04T07:59:44.000Z","uid":75610,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f3d6930d1c91fd46761da2568fa1a895f449f080","tid":979144,"uid":75610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T13:18:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/BlushingSecondHarrier-size_restricted.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FBlushingSecondHarrier-size_restricted.gif&h=3f543daf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇下Announcement trailer先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o77MzDQT1cg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Do77MzDQT1cg&d=VoBFsfm%2BAkNe8%2BlrT9I1H57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=75a29725\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o77MzDQT1cg</a><br />\n<br />\n官網: <a href=\"https://www.hytale.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hytale.com%2F&d=VoBFsfm%2BAkNe8%2BlrT9I1H57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=d71cfc55\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hytale.com/</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1. HYTALE係一隻點嘅game?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n－ <span style=\"color: red;\">沙盒+RPG+有背景故事</span><br />\n－ Procedurally generated world 會有唔同嘅生態環境同detail位<br />\n      &gt;例如海底, 地牢etc.有boss打等等<br />\n      &gt;<span style=\"color: red;\">詳情可以參考官網, trailer同下面條captainsparklez片  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n－起野類似minecraft 亦都有tools support玩家自訂minigame<br />\n<br />\n2. 有啲咩可以做?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n－<span style=\"color: red;\">可以揀你鐘意嘅playstyle</span><br />\n   &gt; Settler, 冒險家, 戰士, 鐵匠, 種田流 , 養動物 etc., 隨著故事發展你可以搵到好多嘢做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n3. 同friend玩得唔得?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n－可以<span style=\"color: red;\"> 隻game support multiplayer</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n&quot;adventure mode is fully playable in co-op: gather a party of friends and combine your skills to leave a mark on the world together&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">CaptainSparklez:</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-qjMasVMkhw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-qjMasVMkhw&d=VoBFsfm%2BAkNe8%2BlrT9I1H57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=32ebb759\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-qjMasVMkhw</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Twitter: <a href=\"http://www.twitter.com/hytale\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitter.com%2Fhytale&d=VoBFsfm%2BAkNe8%2BlrT9I1H57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=b058cc5a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.twitter.com/hytale</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">YouTube: <a href=\"http://youtube.com/hytale\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2Fhytale&d=VoBFsfm%2BAkNe8%2BlrT9I1H57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=9d3f7cc2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://youtube.com/hytale</a></span><br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/hytalegame/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fhytalegame%2F&d=VoBFsfm%2BAkNe8%2BlrT9I1H57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=501a9539\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/hytalegame/</a><br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hytalegame\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhytalegame&d=VoBFsfm%2BAkNe8%2BlrT9I1H57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=88646afc\" data-auto-li